---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import FooterZh from '../../components/FooterZh.astro';

const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('zh-CN', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric'
});
---

<Layout
  title="隐私政策"
  description="L M Precision 私人有限公司的隐私政策。了解我们如何处理您联系我们获取激光雕刻和模具打标服务时的信息。"
  canonicalPath="/zh/privacy/"
  lang="zh"
>

  <Header lang="zh" currentPath="/zh/privacy/" />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 lg:pb-32 relative bg-steel-900/30 min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-steel-700 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-0 w-1/3 h-80 bg-laser/5 blur-[120px] -translate-x-1/4"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-0 w-1/4 h-64 bg-precision-cyan/5 blur-[100px] translate-x-1/4"></div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-laser"></span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-laser uppercase">法律</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
          隐私<span class="text-laser">政策</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-steel-500">
          最后更新: {lastUpdated}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 font-body text-steel-300 leading-relaxed">

        <div class="bg-steel-950 border border-steel-800 p-6 lg:p-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-steel-200">
            L M Precision Engineering 私人有限公司（"我们"）尊重您的隐私。本政策解释我们在您访问我们的网站或联系我们时如何处理信息。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-laser/10 border border-laser/30 text-laser text-sm font-bold">1</span>
            我们收集的信息
          </h2>
          <div class="pl-11 space-y-4">
            <p><strong class="text-white">我们不会自动收集个人信息。</strong>本网站不使用cookies或分析跟踪。</p>
            <p>如果您通过电子邮件或电话直接联系我们，我们只会收到您选择提供的信息（姓名、电子邮件、技术图纸）。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-laser/10 border border-laser/30 text-laser text-sm font-bold">2</span>
            我们如何使用您的信息
          </h2>
          <div class="pl-11 space-y-4">
            <p>当您通过电子邮件向我们发送报价请求时，我们仅使用您的联系信息来：</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-steel-400">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-laser mt-1.5">›</span><span>回复您的询问</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-laser mt-1.5">›</span><span>提供报价</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-laser mt-1.5">›</span><span>就进行中的项目进行沟通</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p>我们不会将您的信息分享给第三方用于营销目的。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-laser/10 border border-laser/30 text-laser text-sm font-bold">3</span>
            数据保留
          </h2>
          <div class="pl-11">
            <p>我们根据运营和法律目的的需要保留业务记录。如需请求删除，请<a href="/zh/#contact" class="text-laser hover:underline">联系我们</a>。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-laser/10 border border-laser/30 text-laser text-sm font-bold">4</span>
            您在PDPA下的权利
          </h2>
          <div class="pl-11 space-y-4">
            <p>根据新加坡的PDPA，您有权访问、更正或撤回对您数据的同意。如需行使这些权利，请<a href="/zh/#contact" class="text-laser hover:underline">联系我们</a>。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <FooterZh />

</Layout>
